com.team.shared.engine.data.user.notification

Class Notifications

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team.shared.engine.data.user.notification.Notifications
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Notifications
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Notifications Collection, wrapped in a special class. Has a Collection field of all the Notifications together.

    Collection of all Notifications that this User has received.

    • Key = Notification.
    • Value = Boolean is shown already.

    annotated with JAXB, to marshal / unmarshal a .xml file.

    Version:
    1.0
